{"type": "article", "id": 45636, "title": "Zara 陷讨薪风波，以及，匡威出了灯芯绒版本 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-28T03:29:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 1425, "name": "Saint Laurent"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 9418, "name": "Luxottica"}, {"id": 2819, "name": "Marc Newson"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170928101531omK3Ix7gFhn2sSbw.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/483227\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧洲委员会开展调查，称眼镜业巨头 Luxottica 和 Essilor 的合并案违反了反垄断法 </strong></a>| 今年一月，意大利顶级眼镜制造商 Luxottica 与法国眼科镜片制造商 Essilor 同意合并，合并后的集团总市值为 460 亿欧元，这是欧洲最大的跨境交易之一。前不久，欧洲委员会对这项合并案开展正式调查，称其违反了反垄断法，该合并案最终能否通过将在 2018 年 2 月 12 日实行最终判决。</p><p><a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/video/%E8%A3%BD%E8%A1%A3%E5%BB%A0%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E5%80%92%E9%96%89-zara%E5%92%8Cmango%E6%8D%B2%E5%85%A5%E8%A8%8E%E8%96%AA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-092200359.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Zara、Mango 陷入讨薪风波</strong></a> | 近日，位于土耳其伊斯坦布尔的制衣工厂 Bravo Tekstil 因 Zara、Mango 终止合约后倒闭，140 名工人被拖欠了 3 个月的薪水和应有的遣散费。据称，拖欠的这笔薪水约 65 万欧元。该工厂此前 75% 的业务量来自 Zara，其余的来自 Mango 和 Next，但这两个品牌均拒绝为工厂的倒闭承担责任。 </p><p>这些工人在土耳其 Clean Clothes Campaign 组织的帮助下在网上发起请愿书，要求消费者支持他们向 Zara 和 Mango 讨回欠薪和遣散费用，目前工人们已获得土耳其法院的支持。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/vans-california-souvenir-pink-embroidered-silk-slip-on\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 带来最新的“花与虎”横须贺鞋款及服装系列</a>，包括 Old Skool 及 Sk8-Hi 鞋款，还有横须贺外套、长袖卫衣、T-Shirt 等多款单品，将于 10 月在 Vans 指定门店上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104511cm30NrkSfpzEDdts.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104511cg1PzA03IqoLGtpl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281045090u4wp5YbaVeSf1dD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104509i8sNmfzynj9TwpYP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104510Dogf5X8ubQmvs0tP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104510jFYdiRgGJXQKk1s6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104511EsxaN574PyfGXJwu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104511tsn5e2jFlq7GbcVE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Puma 与荷兰街头品牌 Daily Paper 合作，带来全新的 2017 秋冬联名系列。</p><p>该系列以 Puma 赞助的非洲足球队为灵感，打造出了一系列足球队服、外套和经典鞋款。</p><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/daily-paper-puma-2017-fall-winter-collaboration\" rel=\"nofollow\">PUMA x Daily Paper 2017 秋冬联名系列</a>现已登陆全球各大 PUMA 与 Daily Paper 门店及指定店铺，据称，此次联名所有营销资金将用于资助在加纳首都阿克拉的阿克拉高级女子学校（Accra Senior Girls School）建立足球场以及相应的配套设施，并为他们的足球队提供队服。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104554uRq91HmZQOz5L8eK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104552KjMRl1GuSYgNx8bk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104556NgUI1WofjuqbvVt4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104558CGv4V3HuFgMqI8ie.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104549JO0VqoSBg46wp7dR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104549zbpiOQhTJWvDH2K5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104550LBZn6rQc8XgTtlDb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281045459kKGg5vhqziZ2FU1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104541VbDUy8ie5QrRXgMp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104542x6VlKq5tXe0mAPWs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104543IEf7xJYtFkrdO0QC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104546N2Jlto4YV5AxTEhy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104551NLBibFMUvWHQa3Ct.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104556gblZO5dNaXo18Jzk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104544s6OpbF0I87hlPVE3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104557nQXYOsjfPIBE9hZk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/asap-nast-converse-collaboration\" rel=\"nofollow\">A$AP Nast 与 Converse 的联名款正式发布</a>。用了今年流行的灯芯绒材质打造 One Star，还有格纹元素搭配毛绒质感鞋带的高筒 Chuck Taylor All Star 70，挺适合秋冬的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104650o2zpJlUyNaxqHWkO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281046536qvS5781y3BewExC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104652TlJo6fpSqkVMxt4E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104653XjLrt8qbfskSReWm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104653kCW3DSR5xBnZrM8l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>工业设计师大师 Marc Newson，为 LV 打造了一个名为<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/27/marc-newson-louis-vuitton-luggage/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Horizon</a> 的行李箱系列。这个系列的行李箱有平整的表面和圆角造型，另外结合了 Monogram 帆布、Damier 石墨纹理、Taiga 皮革等多种花色，售价 3100 美元起。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104723tERb9HP03kCloXQz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104722xnMCrEsqwcFPaOuo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104722FHRfVl2QvIpTNbot.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104724UqT81dnoSOwg5lKa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎时装周，依旧由 <a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/christian-dior-paris-fashion-week-ss18-why-have-there-been-no-great-women-artists/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior</a> 历史上第一位女性创意总监 Maria Grazia Chiuri 操刀的新系列发布。 </p><p>据称这一季的灵感来自童话里的“恶趣味”，还用上了蕾丝、丝绸、皮革、网纱和塑胶材质的结合，出镜率颇高的渔网绑带长靴也成了亮点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104803Fmb6MKLpngoajGOC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104806EKCVxTZ367WdlSa4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092810480443fTxWyiNCwvslz7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104805zCfxALqm2JtZDakY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104806iJP5hs4TqaySEbF1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104806ohwulTctNVGQExPd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104807VkMSYU29nRh4AD6z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104807iy4QnPlwHCmL62Aa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281048083SRDdPwh5QBkGLxE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104810zWCkjib1nqxNV8fp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104810im4jMSGQBf1pwHx7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104810hL6Yw8IWBtsgqmfb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104810nfRIXAMU5upjVgdJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281048113qMeHdS0yK5hrQtW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104811UnTeBRD5a6X9MsLK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104812wndmf0Sjabxv5RKJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104811hLvSkRD9xmMFlyfo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104813vjTPh2AEogHspkFW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104813gcH85dJL4xM2kvWu.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104814QHSyhvgCtnjYRob2.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104814yqUo2LjnkaxpSRZr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104814TdBZ1YroqNRGDQCp.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092810481515Mbmfc6Wrngspok.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281048157KAgY2Gjlzb5TxXc.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104816bjcPpQZFxwBUXiks.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104815haqfuYOw9PQmF0Ws.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/saint-laurent-anthony-vaccarello-ss2018-pfw-eiffel-tower/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saint Laurent </a>的秀展示了 91 套完整的 look，还把秀场搬到了埃菲尔铁塔前，在户外走了一场秀。</p><p>这场秀上的女性元素很多，像是蕾丝、荷叶边、透视、泡泡剪裁以及流苏设计等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104913mTtuzQGAFx7w2YhW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104914fJDwigmrXLe8WknR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104914VuQLhCJeK5FTnjoi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104914o6hSFp7RwkrUJeDY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104914OBvXELIaKnGzfMih.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104927dNs42jcqGIRDJVap.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104928G6Y0uVj9EP3JOHbK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104929v0Oz6cL7FsWhU5dr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104929Gd1BNq0m6WoM4VvE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281049296UE1dLqvfa3gCFZJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104929KVevlBQ1fyjFTdxn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104929mWVedkifnOzPlhjD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928104930eT6kOostW2UfFDYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\